Yeah. So, the resort

27:40.528 --> 27:41.660
is in great condition.

27:41.703 --> 27:43.009
No major debts.

27:43.052 --> 27:44.358
Good. So what's the worry?

27:44.401 --> 27:45.576
Hurricane insurance.

27:45.620 --> 27:47.666
That's why the ask is so low.

27:47.709 --> 27:49.972
You'll just have to get
another million off the price.

27:50.016 --> 27:51.234
You play poker?

27:51.278 --> 27:52.583
Do I... What?

27:52.627 --> 27:54.324
Play poker.

