I want you to meet some friends.

27:56.500 --> 27:58.067
What?

27:58.111 --> 27:59.068
What is this?

27:59.112 --> 28:00.983
Some friends.

28:01.027 --> 28:03.725
It used to be a book group,
but then we got bored, so...

28:03.769 --> 28:05.292
now it's poker.

28:05.335 --> 28:06.728
What friends?

28:08.251 --> 28:10.166
Oh. Oh, my God.

28:10.210 --> 28:12.168
She's a... she's a mogul,
a billionaire.

28:12.212 --> 28:13.648
No.

28:13.692 --> 28:15.519
Half a billion, on a good day.

28:15.563 --> 28:17.434
And.

28:19.219 --> 28:20.742
- As in...?
- Yes.

28:20.786 --> 28:21.743
The performer?

28:21.787 --> 28:23.179
We call her Tee.

28:23.223 --> 28:24.461
She's just like
everyone else here.

28:24.485 --> 28:26.095
Yeah, Bianca, she's-she's not.

28:26.139 --> 28:28.445
- She's...
- Lucca, you're gonna be fine.

28:28.489 --> 28:29.751
You're late.

28:29.795 --> 28:31.753
- This is your friend?
- Yes. Lucca.

28:31.797 --> 28:33.668
This is, , and.

28:33.712 --> 28:35.365
- Hey.
- Hey.
Hi.

28:35.409 --> 28:37.628
I'm-I'm sor...
I didn't know we were...

28:37.672 --> 28:40.414
- coming or I'd have worn pants.-

28:40.457 --> 28:41.850
Okay!

28:41.894 --> 28:43.480
Let's play or I won't have
timeto kick your asses.

28:43.504 --> 28:45.767
- I'm not really that much
of a poker player.

28:45.811 --> 28:47.682
Oh, we mostly play for charity.

28:47.726 --> 28:49.118
Where are we starting the pot,

28:49.162 --> 28:51.120
- ten or 20?
- Last time, we did 20.

28:51.164 --> 28:54.210
Uh, Bianca,
can I ask a question?

28:55.255 --> 28:56.386
Um...

28:56.430 --> 28:58.345
"Ten or 20," that's...?

28:58.388 --> 29:00.347
- Thousand.
- Yeah, I'm gonna watch.

